{
  "stem": "11797.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He learned how to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was a-- he was a very handy guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was already about-- I was 19 already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was about 17.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was very small, too, then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Very tiny.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This camp mostly making the foxholes, work in the yard, work in-- in-- fixing-- taking one stone, another stone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Going out from the camp, going out, workinig in the-- in the muds, cleaning the-- cleaning the mud-- mud puddles, you know, from the water, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Working the fields, picking up corn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Corn.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For growing corn.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just the growing corn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So maybe then we used to help, I don't know, pick them up and-- and put them in bags, you know, someplace, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we-- we used to-- mostly it was-- was very manual, hard work you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you don't eat nothing, it becomes even harder.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gave us this piece of bread at night, now, in order to eat it tomorrow morning, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of people who ate it the same time didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in the morning when they gave them the black coffee, they needed the bread from last night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They didn't have it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They only drank black coffee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's how they didn't make it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When you were in the corn fields, did you have a chance to eat some corn?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father, he stoled about four corns, put it under his shirts, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I cannot explain to you how unmercifully he was beaten, my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was skinny.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was trying to bring in three or four just for us, you know, just to eat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He ?] [? had ?] [INAUDIBLE], they caught him doing that.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
